    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073310/extras/33afdc0c578a74a3dc24a51240578331.avif?t=1732757980\" width=616 height=196 /></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073310/extras/cc39fe8ef9ffbe950288f51ebedf9e72.avif?t=1732757980\" width=616 height=196 /></span></p>Become the ultimate manager of tomorrow's superstars with &quot;K-Pop!&quot;, an addictive clicker game created by stans for stans! Gather billions of fans, unlock idols at every milestone, compare your score with your friends and become the ultimate k-pop manager. <br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073310/extras/0200dda6fe5b0003aef4f8f506ff2f81.avif?t=1732757980\" width=616 height=196 /></span></p>Trade idol cards with your friends and with the community on the marketplace, display your collection on your Steam profile! Show us your rarest bias! <br><br><strong>Play 3 hours to collect idols across six levels of rarity:</strong> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Common</li><li>Uncommon</li><li>Rare</li><li>Epic</li><li>Legendary</li><li>Genuine</li></ul><br><strong>At every milestone, a new random idol joins your group!</strong> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>100 fans</li><li>1000 fans</li><li>10.000 fans</li><li>100.000 fans</li><li>1.000.000 fans</li><li>10.000.000 fans</li><li>100.000.000 fans</li><li>1.000.000.000 fans</li><li>10.000.000.000 fans</li><li>100.000.000.000 fans</li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073310/extras/b8db7ba744fa0b08c299a1dc145b9371.avif?t=1732757980\" width=616 height=196 /></span></p>Play during regular updates and special events that introduce new idols and cards based on real-life events, such as album releases, concerts, anniversaries, and fan meetings. Stay tuned for exclusive content when your favorite groups release new music or celebrate milestones! <br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073310/extras/699dbebc08834dd1a34f114de1bb78e7.avif?t=1732757980\" width=616 height=196 /></span></p>Compare your progress with other players worldwide and fight for the top 30 spots on the leaderboard! Show who is the ultimate K-Pop stan. <br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073310/extras/0b867cfc6ad7eeb14f647c193d07a87c.avif?t=1732757980\" width=616 height=196 /></span></p>",
